{"product_id": "39200", "page": 18, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-06-06", "text": "I've started playing Dunegon Siege II as a continuation to my adventure on the first one, and even if it has some points in which it does not remind its antecessor, it's really nice to see how you get stronger by each chapter that passes.\nDS II may be a 10-year-old game, but it easily surpasses in difficulty and gameplay some of the games nowadays (do not expect much of the graphics since it's from 2005)\nI recommend this game to people looking for an RPG similar to Diablo and that look for a very good background storywith lots of sidequests.", "hours": 44.4, "user_id": "76561198044754587", "username": "Suco de fruta", "products": 496, "early_access": false}
