{"product_id": "39200", "page": 18, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-05-29", "text": "I was looking for a basic dungeon game with a skill tree, treasure, and magic items to augment your character.  I just wanted a game to dive into and kill some time.  This game is the perfect fit.  I've only played it for a couple of hours, but I really like it.  The world is pretty fluid, I love the click to move, treasure is realistic, and though I'm playing easy mode, it's not extremely easy.  Kiting is realistic as the AI will follow you for a bit, then give up on you.  What a steal it is at $6.99, thanks Steam.", "hours": 22.5, "user_id": "76561198026850548", "username": "Swing", "products": 41, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
