{"product_id": "39200", "page": 34, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-18", "text": "Immersion at its finest. What DS 1 should have been. Improved what the 1st game had to offer in basically every aspect. It is indeed a huge timesink but thats what translates to great RPG's. To me it is one of those rare timeless masterpieces.", "hours": 67.6, "user_id": "76561198076558850", "username": "La Volpe", "products": 913, "early_access": false}
