{"product_id": "39200", "page": 35, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-10-06", "text": "The game begins pretty cool. You are part of an invasion force working for the bad guys.  Now that is awesome!  I thought the developers came up with an interesting story, where you are not saving the world like in EVERY other Rpg.\nBut immidiately after the introduction you get captured by gay elves. And from then on you are working for the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing elves. Was a bit disappointed by that.\nIt is still a good game, though I didn\u00b4t like it as much as the first Dungeon Siege. Graphics and gameplay are almost the same in both titles. So if you have the choice of getting DS1 or DS2, better choose the first.", "hours": 73.0, "user_id": "76561198082987433", "username": "simest", "products": 142, "early_access": false}
