{"product_id": "39200", "page": 39, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-04-15", "text": "I have played Dungeon Siege since middle school. I am incredibly happy that it was ported to Steam. The only flaw with this game is when the franchise was acquired by Square and put into Steam, they did not implement multiplayer or modding. Either way, the campaign is great.", "hours": 12.9, "username": "iareth0m", "products": 132, "early_access": false}
