{"product_id": "39200", "page": 39, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-04-13", "text": "Having played through DS1/2 before a few years ago, I got this as part of a package deal (DS1,2,3) and didn't notice that it didn't include all the DLC/xpacs.\nIMHO if you're going to play Dungeon Siege 1 or 2, you play it with all the DLC/xpacs. Even more so if you're going to play it in multiplayer, which simply doesn't work as is in the STEAM version.\nIf anything, they probably bundled this to get people into buying DS3, which is nothing like Dungeon Siege 1 or 2.", "hours": 0.1, "user_id": "76561198025701675", "username": "Bhun", "products": 83, "early_access": false}
