{"product_id": "39200", "page": 42, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-30", "text": "No bugs, nice texture and graphics, possibility to learn every skill if you train them, and lots of features making this game verry fun to play it take about 60-80 hours to finish all quest in the low difficulty, then you can keep playing and growing your char in the other difficult (New Game +).\nThis game remind me all the hours spend to clear some wet caves in Dungeon Siege I.\nIts verry similar and so it is a solid 9/10 (yes, even if this game is 10 years old)", "hours": 70.5, "username": "Pugwis", "products": 59, "early_access": false}
