{"product_id": "39200", "page": 42, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-25", "text": "Dungeon Siege 2 represents a great squad-based action role-playing game, which contains all of the best elements of its predecessor, and introduces novelties like the class based super powers and class related skill trees.\nIt is rounded out by smart combat mechanics, an impressive storyline and immersive atmosphere. The higher difficulties will keep you entertained with new challenges, while the loot will be improving continuously.\nThe game has no Steam achievements.", "hours": 77.2, "user_id": "76561197968514473", "username": "Meat-King\u00a9\u00ae", "products": 424, "early_access": false}
